  "title": "Assistant Engineer [Field Service] - Industrial Equipment & Instrumentation | 5 Days!! [0580]",
  "description": "<p>Working Salary : $2500 - $3000 + $140 Allowance<br />Working Days: Mon - Fri | 8.30 - 5.30pm<br />Working Location: Tampines<br /><br /><strong>Job Summary:</strong><br />Field Service Assistant Engineer (FSAE) will be responsible for commissioning, maintenance and troubleshooting of field instrumentation products Job<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Providing technical support to field service teams</li><li>Supporting Factory Acceptance test and Site Acceptance test</li><li>Maintaining accurate and reliable service tool inventory</li><li>Completing service documentation is completed in proper format and by due dates- this includes items such as timesheets, service/repair reports, follow ups, daily logs, expenses, etc.</li><li>Ensuring proper storage of engineering documentation- drawings, version history, scope documents, RFI's Job</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / ITE Certificate in <strong>Instrumentation / CPT / Electronics / Mechatronic Engineering</strong></li><li>Min. 2 years of related experience in Instrumentation</li><li>Good knowledge of machine operation and machine construction</li><li>Experience in handling with high <strong>vacuum equipments, pumps, chillers, and compressors</strong></li><li>Able to interpret maintenance manuals, schematics, and wiring diagrams</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
